{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21061.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":100,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Arisa","nameRight":"Chisato","textRight":"*Giggle*","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":403401}],"textRight":"There was a lot of arguing, but those three@seem like they're great friends."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":1}],"textRight":"They remind me of us quite a bit."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Hm? Really?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401}],"textRight":"Yes, except that there are four of us."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":200}],"textRight":"\"Keep standing around like that and we'll@leave you behind!\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401}],"textRight":"That sounds so much like something you@would say."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Oh come on."},{"chara":[{"id":403301}],"textLeft":"Just what kinda person do you take me for?"},{"chara":[{"id":403401,"motion":300}],"textRight":"Well, let's see."},{"chara":[{"id":403401,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Not the best communicator, but a girl who@treasures her friends more than anyone else."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"[chara:403301:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":403401}],"textRight":"Because no one would even say that if they@really were going to leave someone behind."},{"chara":[{"id":403401}],"textRight":"I think if we got separated, you'd wait for@me no matter how long it took."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"Wh-what are you talking about?! I'm not@that nice, you know!"},{"chara":[{"id":403401,"motion":200}],"textRight":"See? There's that act again."},{"chara":[{"id":403401}],"textRight":"That's the reason why you're always@misunderstood!"},{"chara":[{"id":403401,"motion":100}],"textRight":"But it's all right."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403401}],"textRight":"I told you the day we met, didn't I? That@it's still not too late."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"..."},{"nameNarration":"Arisa","narration":"Yeah, it was that smile.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"That's what saved me from my loneliness."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4033_00_03"}],"nameCenter":"Arisa","textCenter":"Come on, Chisato. Are you trying to make@me remember those days?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":300}]},{"chara":[{"id":403301}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}